divs: Sighting DetailsDriving North on I-75 just before Wesley Chapel, FL when I spotted a bright light in the sky. Figure was cross shaped with white blinking lights on each end and a very bright light in the middle. Object was stationary or slow moving. Object looked small so had to be at high altitude.
Summary: Strange object flying near Tampa North Airport
